OL,3,CMP stands down so Andy Burnham 'can
OL,4,Cfight to re-enter Parliament'
OL,6,FJosh Simons MP has announced he is
OL,7,Fstanding down so that "Andy Burnham
OL,8,Fcan fight to re-enter Parliament".
OL,10,FIn a statement, the Makerfield MP
OL,11,Fsaid: "Today, I am putting the people
OL,12,FI represent and the country I love
OL,13,Ffirst and will be resigning as MP for
OL,14,FMakerfield.
OL,16,F"I am standing aside so that Andy
OL,17,FBurnham can return to his home, fight
OL,18,Fto re-enter Parliament, and if
OL,19,Felected, drive the change our country
OL,20,Fis crying out for."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
