PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778789155
OL,3,CMP stands down so Andy Burnham 'can
OL,4,Cfight to re-enter Parliament'
OL,6,FAndy Burnham confirmed he would be
OL,7,Frequesting the permission of Labour's
OL,8,FNEC to stand in the Makerfield by-
OL,9,Felection.
OL,11,FIn a statement on X, the Greater
OL,12,FManchester Mayor saying a "much bigger
OL,13,Fchange is needed at a national level".
OL,15,FMr Burnham said: "I will work hard to
OL,16,Fregain the trust of people in the
OL,17,FMakerfield constituency, many of whom
OL,18,Fhave long supported our party but lost
OL,19,Ffaith in recent times.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778789155
OL,3,CMP stands down so Andy Burnham 'can
OL,4,Cfight to re-enter Parliament'
OL,6,F"We will change Labour for the better
OL,7,Fand make it a party you can believe in
OL,8,Fagain."
OL,10,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester has
OL,11,Flong been seen as a potential rival to
OL,12,FSir Keir Starmer, but he has been
OL,13,Funable to officially challenge the
OL,14,FPrime Minister because he is not a
OL,15,Fsitting MP.
OL,17,FAndy Burnham previously attempted to
OL,18,Fstand as the Labour candidate in the
OL,19,FGorton and Denton by-election, but his
OL,20,Fbid was blocked by Labour's National
OL,21,FExecutive Committee.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778789155
OL,3,CMP stands down so Andy Burnham 'can
OL,4,Cfight to re-enter Parliament'
OL,6,FThe committee cited the cost to the
OL,7,Ftax payer and the party if a Mayoral
OL,8,Felection was to take place to replace
OL,9,FMr Burnham as the Mayor of Greater
OL,10,FManchester.
OL,12,FBut a number of critics accused the
OL,13,FPrime Minister of blocking Andy
OL,14,FBurnham's attempt to run out of fear
OL,15,Fhe would mount a leadership challenge
OL,16,Fif he made it Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
