OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778789155
OL,3,CMP stands down so Andy Burnham 'can
OL,4,Cfight to re-enter Parliament'
OL,6,FFormer Deputy Leader and Ashton-under-
OL,7,FLyne MP Angela Rayner expressed her
OL,8,Fconcern over the Prime Minister's
OL,9,Fleadership, and said the decision to
OL,10,Fblock Mr Burnham from running as an MP
OL,11,Fwas a "mistake".
OL,13,FReform UK has promised to "throw
OL,14,Fabsolutely everything" at a by-
OL,15,Felection in Makerfield, where Labour
OL,16,FMP Josh Simons has announced he will
OL,17,Fstand down to allow Greater Manchester
OL,18,FMayor Andy Burnham a path back to
OL,19,FParliament.
OL,26,@uD@[OUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
