FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778789155
OL,3,CMP stands down so Andy Burnham 'can
OL,4,Cfight to re-enter Parliament'
OL,6,FNigel Farage, the leader of Reform,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We look forward to the contest
OL,8,Fand we will throw absolutely
OL,9,Feverything at it."
OL,11,FFollowing a disastrous local election
OL,12,Fresult for Labour which saw a large
OL,13,Fgroup of traditional red wall voters
OL,14,Fin the North West turn to Reform,
OL,15,Fthere have been growing calls for the
OL,16,FPrime Minister to resign or set out a
OL,17,Ftimeline for his departure and allow a
OL,18,Fleadership contest to take place.
OL,26,@oD@GOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
