FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778789155
OL,3,CMP stands down so Andy Burnham 'can
OL,4,Cfight to re-enter Parliament'
OL,6,FWhile a number of MPs have backed Andy
OL,7,FBurnham's return to Westminster, the
OL,8,Fself-styled "King of the North" will
OL,9,Fstill need approval from the NEC to
OL,10,Frun as the Labour candidate in the
OL,11,Fupcoming by-election. The committee,
OL,12,Fwhich includes the Prime Minister,
OL,13,Fblocked his previous bid 8-1 with
OL,14,Fdeputy leader and Manchester Central
OL,15,FMP Lucy Powell the only member to back
OL,16,Fhim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
