OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778789155
OL,3,CMP stands down so Andy Burnham 'can
OL,4,Cfight to re-enter Parliament'
OL,6,FIf Mayor Burnham is named as Labour's
OL,7,Fcandidate, it will mean he goes back
OL,8,Fon a pledge he made after being re-
OL,9,Felected in 2024 to stay in the role
OL,10,Ffor an entire third term.
OL,12,FThe decision would also trigger a
OL,13,FMayoral election in Greater Manchester
OL,14,Fwhich would see Reform, the Greens,
OL,15,Fand the Liberal Democrats all fight to
OL,16,Fcapitalise on their gains in the 2026
OL,17,Flocal elections across the city region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
